when she saw me before.

221
00:09:08,765 --> 00:09:10,631
She wasn't mad at
you. She was confused.

222
00:09:10,700 --> 00:09:12,900
There's something in her
head that they needed to fix,

223
00:09:12,936 --> 00:09:14,068
and they've done that.

224
00:09:14,137 --> 00:09:16,171
She's back to
her old self again.

225
00:09:21,244 --> 00:09:22,576
You sure?

226
00:09:24,664 --> 00:09:26,481
I don't know 100%, Ethan,

227
00:09:26,550 --> 00:09:29,134
but I think we should try, okay?

228
00:09:31,538 --> 00:09:32,887
All right.

229
00:09:40,213 --> 00:09:41,312
Ethan?

230
00:09:41,381 --> 00:09:42,981
You're okay?

231
00:09:44,117 --> 00:09:46,751
Come here.

232
00:09:50,373 --> 00:09:51,906
Oh.

233
00:09:51,974 --> 00:09:53,140
Oh, God.

234
00:09:53,209 --> 00:09:54,992
I love you so much.

235
00:09:56,546 --> 00:09:58,362
Did you get hurt?

236
00:09:58,431 --> 00:09:59,731
No?

237
00:10:00,901 --> 00:10:02,834
You look really good.

238
00:10:06,022 --> 00:10:07,622
My car crash mom woke up.

239
00:10:07,691 --> 00:10:10,758
And the lawyer sent over
an e-mail with the forms.

240
00:10:10,827 --> 00:10:12,994
We need two names, a
guardian and a backup.

241
00:10:13,063 --> 00:10:14,762
Before it was Lexie,
Cristina, and Owen.

242
00:10:14,831 --> 00:10:16,509
So Cristina and then
which one of your sisters

243
00:10:16,533 --> 00:10:17,773
do you want as a backup?

244
00:10:17,834 --> 00:10:19,267
