It's Zola and fetus.

246
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:22,921
Stop calling the baby fetus.

247
00:10:22,990 --> 00:10:25,390
Well, she will love him
whatever his name is.

248
00:10:25,425 --> 00:10:27,408
All right, talk to her
and see what she says.

249
00:10:27,494 --> 00:10:28,893
I know what she'll say.

250
00:10:28,945 --> 00:10:31,585
